{"tid":2514474,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[有片]比利時駐南韓大使的中国人妻子掌摑首爾女店員  引發外交風波","createTime":"2021-05-03T09:33:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T11:29:07.000Z","uid":204533,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"9d8a63451c1e012fea0363e3d49870c8dd34b71d","tid":2514474,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:33:57.000Z","msg":"//南韓首爾女店員遭比利時駐韓大使的中國籍夫人掌摑而引發的外交風波，至今將近一個月，除大使代妻在Facebook道歉外，涉案女主角、太極高手相雪秋，事後聲稱中風入院，至今仍未公開露面。據悉，大使夫人已在上月23日出院。《蘋果》特約記者日前到訪事發服裝店，遇襲的女店員正受耳鳴及情緒困擾，無法受訪，但其丈夫對《蘋果》表示，妻子除受大使夫人掌摑外，後腦亦遭拍打，他批評大使的道歉「缺乏誠意」，不是大使夫人親自道歉，他們不會接受。//<br />\n<br />\n//<strong><span class=\"red\">相雪秋1958年生於北京，中國名校畢業，在聯合國駐布魯塞爾辦事處的歐盟環境部工作了4年</span></strong>。2018年起隨丈夫萊斯庫耶赴南韓。她在20歲時接觸太極拳，有太極教練聘書，先後在菲律賓、立陶宛、韓國等地擔任過太極拳教練。（香港《蘋果動新聞》南韓直擊）//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210503/EZ36NWE3ERGVRCRY5IUOX542UA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210503%2FEZ36NWE3ERGVRCRY5IUOX542UA%2F&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOFEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=980434f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210503%2FEZ36NWE3ERGVRCRY5IUOX542UA%2F&h=0baaedfa\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210503/EZ36NWE3ERGVRCRY5IUOX542UA/</a>"},{"pid":"6b0cf88276fcd613312ae7f5aee304e2eba334ae","tid":2514474,"uid":204533,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:35:20.000Z","msg":"原來中国功夫真係好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images.edigest.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/202104221206033327760737053_7669423746080f62bb0608-1024x576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.edigest.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F202104221206033327760737053_7669423746080f62bb0608-1024x576.jpg&h=ff154eae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"61c7c3950d3038d620ba819191c25f7d1fe69d28","tid":2514474,"uid":204533,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"